Other special acts in criminal law
The provisions of the Danish Criminal Code regarding sexual offences
went through essential amendments taking effect from 1 July 2013. The
amendments resulted in e.g. more categories of sexual offences than
previously being placed under the provisions about rape (section
216). See more in the documentation of statistics, in the chapter
